458
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ja imam problem.

459
00:42:05,440 --> 00:42:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mogu sad kod tebe doći tu.

460
00:42:07,119 --> 00:42:09,280
